Name: aluminium, ingot, primary, import from EU27 & EFTA | aluminium, primary, ingot | EN15804GD, U
Category: C:Manufacturing/24:Manufacture of basic metals/242:Manufacture of basic precious and other non-ferrous metals/2420:Manufacture of basic precious and other non-ferrous metals
Description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/22772/documentation

This dataset represents the amount of imported primary aluminium from Europe (EU27 & EFTA) to North America. The import value is valid for 2016 and includes all imports, independently whether used within the importing region, or re-exported. AA and AAC statistics

This activity represents the point of "handing over" the primary aluminium ingot from one country to the other at the border.
